I like pastors at Nairobi’s Citam (Christ is the Answer Ministries) because of their practical, as opposed to dogmatic, approach to preaching. They address issues of the here and now before they tell us about the hereafter. 

One of my favourites is the former bishop of the church, David Oginde. My other great was Pastor Dennis White, who has since returned to his country of origin, Canada. 



